title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: Pokkiri Simon
subTitle: Simon, an ardent Vijay fan, along with his friends, crosses paths with Arjunan and his brother who are petty criminals. Later, he decides to fight Arjunan and end his reign in the city.

title: Nizhal
subTitle: John, a judge, struggles to recover from a traumatic accident and crosses paths with Nithin, a young boy. When Nithin's stories about murder are found to be true, John sets out to investigate them.

title: Dhamaka
subTitle: Things get complicated when Swami and Anand, two look-alike men from different backgrounds, fall in love with the same girl.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Sthanarthi Sreekuttan
subTitle: Sreekuttan and Ambadi present an intense rivalry concerning a school election. Soon, the contest fundamentally affects the classroom and involves pride and friendship.

title: A.R.M
subTitle: Tied to the history of an ancient relic, Ajayan faces the consequences of his forefathers' decisions and their cascading fates.

title: Hello Mummy
subTitle: Boney falls for Stefy, but her mother's ghost disapproves. However, he tries to overcome this supernatural hurdle to win Stefy's hand in marriage.

title: Avihitham
subTitle: Prakashan, after drinking, encounters Vinod and a young woman near a carpenter's abode. Subsequently, both men, Prakashan and Venu, perceive this duo as an affectionate couple, suspecting the woman is Nirmala.

title: Neyyattinkara Gopante Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: Neyyattinkara Gopante Aaraattu

title: Natturajavu
subTitle: Pulikkattil, an affluent family man, is forced to bear the brunt and burden of his late father's unscrupulous past. Now, Karnan, a jail convict, decides to settle some old scores with him.

title: Aagathan
subTitle: En route to Bangalore, a man falls in love with a beautiful girl. But he soon realises that her father was responsible for the death of his sister during a terrorist attack a long time ago.

title: Kadha Thudarunnu
subTitle: Vidyalakshmi struggles to lead a normal life with her daughter after the sudden death of her husband. However, her world transforms after meeting Preman, an auto-rickshaw driver.

title: Thanthonni
subTitle: Kochu, an alcoholic, is a member of the Vadakkan Veettil family who leaves them after a fight. He later comes home for his share when their wealth is being divided.

title: Kalippattam
subTitle: A violinist enters a marriage that promises security, only to face heartbreak as love, illness and time reshape everything he once believed was under control.

title: Summer in Bethlehem
subTitle: Ravishankar pretends to own the farmhouse of his friend Dennis when his relatives pay a visit along with their granddaughters. Chaos ensues after his prospective bride confesses her love for Dennis.

title: Pushpa: The Rise - Part 1
subTitle: As Pushpa, a labourer, rises in the world of red sandalwood smuggling, he ends up making many enemies. However, violence ensues when the police try to topple his illegal business.

title: Premalu
subTitle: Having been rejected once, Sachin, a young man, falls for Reenu, a girl he meets during a wedding, and sets out to win her over.

title: Grrr...
subTitle: Heartbroken and intoxicated, Rejimon stumbles into a lion's den at the zoo. Haridas, a guard, has to forcefully dive in to rescue him, earning media attention for the blunder.

title: Grrr...

title: China Town
subTitle: Mathukutty, Zachariah and Binoy, whose fathers were friends twenty years ago, return to Goa in order to reclaim a casino. But they face many challenges when a local goon tries to plot against them.

title: Irul
subTitle: Alex and Archana go on a trip but soon their car breaks down and they take shelter at a nearby house. However, things take a turn when the owner of the house behaves in a suspicious manner.

title: Kaththi
subTitle: A fugitive encounters his doppelganger and plots to steal his identity for a quick escape. However, fate intervenes as he chooses to embrace and fight for his look-alike's mission.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Oru Indian Pranayakadha
subTitle: Aymanam Sidharthan, a leader of the youth wing of a local political party, hopes to succeed in politics. Irene, an Indo-Canadian woman making a documentary on Indian politics, is smitten with him.

title: Snehaveedu
subTitle: Ajayan comes back to his village to be with his ailing mother. However, things get strange when a boy comes to his house claiming to be his son.

title: Keshu Ee Veedinte Nadhan
subTitle: The life of an ordinary driver Keshu turns upside down when he wins a lottery worth 12 crores but his morality gets tested.

title: Natturajavu
subTitle: Pulikkattil, an affluent family man, is forced to bear the brunt and burden of his late father's unscrupulous past. Now, Karnan, a jail convict, decides to settle some old scores with him.

title: Thug Life
subTitle: Gang leader Sakthivel adopts Amaran after a gang war, but years later, a survival from assassination sparks doubt. Soon, Sakthivel suspects Amaran, igniting a conflict of loyalty and revenge.

title: Kannur Squad
subTitle: Determined to catch a notorious criminal, a police officer and his team undergoes several challenges as they scale the lengths of the country.
